title: Paris Hilton

description:
Icon Paris Hilton comes on Good For You and Whitney makes good on her promise to only ask questions Paris hasn't fielded before.  Therapy?  ADD meds?  Biggest fear?  And Dan Levy calls in for a surprise facetime.  To kick things off Whitney, Benton, and Emily talk butt implants and getting roofied.
